OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FRail strike: Agency staff  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fcould cover future         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fdisruption                 
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The government is preparing plans to   
OL,6, repeal a legal ban on agency staff     
OL,7, filling in for striking workers.       
OL,9,FTransport Secretary Grant Shapps told  
OL,10,Fthe Sunday Telegraph a potential change
OL,11,Fin legislation could allow companies to
OL,12,Fhire temporary workers to cover some   
OL,13,Froles and prevent disruption.          
OL,15,FAny intervention would not affect the  
OL,16,Frail strikes across Britain this month.
OL,18,FBut Mr Shapps said changes could be    
OL,19,Fbrought in quickly to minimise future  
OL,20,Faction in rail or other sectors.       
